Description_lang: Awakens the powers of Etheralus rings worn by you and your allies, increasing healing and absorption done by ${$<WarlordsTrinketNerf>*$m1/100}% for $187618d. When this effect ends, each empowered player unleashes a burst of energy that shields your allies, absorbing damage equal to ${$m1/100}% of all healing done while empowered, divided evenly among the shielded players. (2 min shared cooldown)
